DELETE FROM jobs WHERE id IN (SELECT id FROM jobs ORDER BY id DESC LIMIT 5);

This ensures your database is cleanly optimized down to **5 candidates and 15 jobs** ($5 \times 15 = 75$ pairings total), allowing you to run your tests swiftly without any local GPU timeouts! Run the updated seeder and execute the SQL script in your browser to begin testing.</sql><current_tab id="0"/></tab_sql></sqlb_project>
